<div class="msgContentFrame">I would say it isn't self-pity, but indulgence. Everyone has moments where they feel sorry for themselves, but it's wallowing in them and not looking past them that'll land you in trouble.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><span class="sm">And still I see no changes can't a brother get a little peace <br />It's war on the streets &amp; the war in the Middle East</span></div><!--[if IE 7]><hr class="msgIE7fill"/><![endif]--></div>
