<div class="msgWhoFrame"><div class="msgUM"><a class="msgWhoName Guru" href="/poster.html?user=255194">Mistress DSD</a><div class="msgWhoTitle Guru">Caffeine Queen</div><div class="msgUMex"><a href="/db/journal.html?user=255194" class="icon-userjournal">User's Journal</a></div></div><div class="msgAvatar"><img alt="Avatar" height="120" width="114" src="http://common.allakhazam.com/images/uf/DSD/DSD_allahs.jpg" /></div><div class="msgStar"><span class="bright">There is no 5th star.</span></div><div class="msgWhoNum">12779 posts</div>
